These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, malaysian
1. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
2. the nigerian is on the right of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Nationality   | malaysian | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, amaryllis
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Flower   | bellflower | amaryllis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, paramedic
1. the paramedic is on the left or right of the teacher##3
2. the paramedic is on the left of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Job   | paramedic | teacher |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
