1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Sport   | lacrosse | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-5::.
